1. *Kofer* mi je bio pretežak da ga ponosim sam (My *suitcase* was too heavy to carry it alone).
2. Molim vas, donesite mi *kofer* sa polica (Please, bring me the *suitcase* from the shelves).
3. Nisam siguran da će se sve stvari stići staviti u ovaj *kofer* (I'm not sure if all things will fit in this *suitcase*).
4. Možete li mi pomoći da spakujem ovaj *kofer*? (Can you help me pack this *suitcase*?)
5. Nisam mogao da otvorim *kofer* jer sam zaboravio lozinku (I couldn't open the *suitcase* because I forgot the password).
6. Moja omiljena boja za *kofer* je tamno plava (My favorite color for a *suitcase* is dark blue).
7. *Koferi* su bili spakovani, pa smo krenuli na aerodrom (The *suitcases* were packed, so we headed to the airport).
8. Našli su *kofer* na aerodromu i vratili ga vlasniku (They found the *suitcase* at the airport and returned it to the owner).
9. Zbog iznenadne promene plana, morao sam da otkažem svoju rezervaciju *kofera* (Due to a sudden change of plans, I had to cancel my *suitcase* reservation).
10. Naš *kofer* se izgubio na putu i nikada nije pronađen (Our *suitcase* got lost on the way and was never found).